{"4011180": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "NTR偶像: Déjà Vu", "steam_appid": 4011180, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4011180/extras/3dc696245b04ca54ff685782de6a3efa.avif?t=1776137903\" width=1560 height=1040 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2>在NTR偶像: Déjà Vu，你可以在微小差距的平行世界裡，體驗「NTR偶像」的事件。<br>玩家將扮演經紀人，將「事務所」裡的偶像新人「艾莉」，<br>進行「特殊培養」以及偶像事業的「潛規則」，<br>並讓男友「哈里」見證她從「清純少女」逐步成為「資深偶像」的過程。 <br>以及還有意想不到的偶像結局等著玩家探索！<br><br><br><strong>艾莉</strong><br>天真無邪的少女走向歷練成熟的女性<br>「我是艾莉，今年20歲！興趣是唱歌跳舞，希望有朝一日可以成為一名偶像！」<br>「嘿嘿…我也沒有那麼厲害拉！」<br>「不行…不要改變哈里在裡面的形狀…不可以！咿啊啊！」<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4011180/extras/d9e4b01c3bcfcd080c699af58f5d0976.poster.avif?t=1776137903\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4011180/extras/d9e4b01c3bcfcd080c699af58f5d0976.webm?t=1776137903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4011180/extras/d9e4b01c3bcfcd080c699af58f5d0976.mp4?t=1776137903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>希凝</strong><br>傳說級的大偶像，也擔任新人偶像的指導教師，神秘且成熟的女性<br>「哎呀呀，小艾莉也太有姿色了吧，尤其是胸部，特別想讓人捏兩下呢。」<br>「別怕別怕，小艾莉這麼可愛，我可是買了三本呢，一本收藏、一本觀賞、一本實用。」<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4011180/extras/f2b94a61bbcceb8778fbd0e9f9f6899c.poster.avif?t=1776137903\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4011180/extras/f2b94a61bbcceb8778fbd0e9f9f6899c.webm?t=1776137903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea